@startuml
[*] --> ReadyForCard
ReadyForCard : entry / nil
ReadyForCard : do / wait for card insertion
ReadyForCard : exit / card inserted

ReadyForCard --> CardInserted : card inserted
CardInserted : entry / nil
CardInserted : do / prompt for PIN
CardInserted : exit / PIN entered

CardInserted --> PINVerified : PIN verified successfully
CardInserted --> PINIncorrect : PIN verification failed

PINVerified : entry / nil
PINVerified : do / provide transaction options
PINVerified : exit / user selects option

PINVerified --> ProcessingWithdrawal : withdrawal selected
ProcessingWithdrawal : entry / nil
ProcessingWithdrawal : do / process withdrawal request
ProcessingWithdrawal : exit / cash dispensed

ProcessingWithdrawal --> CashDispensed : cash dispensed
CashDispensed : entry / nil
CashDispensed : do / print receipt
CashDispensed : exit / receipt printed

CashDispensed --> ReceiptPrinted : receipt printed
ReceiptPrinted : entry / nil
ReceiptPrinted : do / return card
ReceiptPrinted : exit / card returned

ReceiptPrinted --> CardReturned : card returned
CardReturned : entry / nil
CardReturned : do / reset system
CardReturned : exit / system ready for next user

CardReturned --> ReadyForCard : system reset
@enduml
